{
  "stem": "19807.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And so I-- I was always super protective with him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And then when the landlady's daughter came back from Germany, they had-- we had to leave that house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we went to live in another house, of which I have a picture that just came back from Bulgaria.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So basically, my brother, wherever I went, I always grabbed him with me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one time, I remember that some kids picked on him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I ran after that kid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and he was just about to go into his house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I took a large stick and I just threw that stick, hit him in-- in the legs.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he just fell.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I could hear the screams so I ran to stay with my-- my aunt for two days.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was afraid to come home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was always protective of my-- of my kid brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then when I-- when he was, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] well, seven years old, then I left for Israel, from Bulgaria.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I did not see him for five years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, I was with him only two years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I married and I came to-- to-- to this country.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- but when I was in-- in Israel, I made sure that he went and he studied in [NON-ENGLISH] and then in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Those were very good schools.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They work half a day, they study half a day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I wanted him to study English and-- because my-- my wife was American.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she taught me how important it would be for them to study English, as well as you know that today in Israel, practically everybody speaks English.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But he would not learn that.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
